<view class="page">
  <view class="notice-bar">
    <view class="notice-icon">营业中</view>
    <view class="muted">开业活动全场 88 折，营业时间 {{shop.hours}}，支持配送和到店自提。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card hero">
    <image class="image hero-image" src="{{heroImage}}" mode="aspectFill" binderror="handleHeroImageError"></image>
    <view class="hero-overlay">
      <view class="hero-copy-shell">
        <view class="hero-copy-panel">
          <view class="hero-term">{{seasonTheme.name}}</view>
          <view class="hero-tip">{{seasonTheme.tip}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="hero-brand">炖时光</view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-hit-area" bindtap="handleLogoTap"></view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="grid-2 quick-grid">
      <view class="quick-item" bindtap="goTo" data-page="menu">
        <view class="icon-circle">点</view>
        <view class="quick-title">开始点单</view>
        <view class="quick-desc">炖汤、面食、套餐都能直接选，不用再手写备注。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="quick-item" bindtap="goTo" data-page="member">
        <view class="icon-circle">会</view>
        <view class="quick-title">会员权益</view>
        <view class="quick-desc">积分抵扣、老客优惠、充值活动都放在这里。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="quick-item" bindtap="copyAddress">
        <view class="icon-circle">路</view>
        <view class="quick-title">复制地址</view>
        <view class="quick-desc">位置在意库 66 栋，暖心素火锅隔壁。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="quick-item" bindtap="previewQr">
        <view class="icon-circle">联</view>
        <view class="quick-title">联系店长</view>
        <view class="quick-desc">售后、改单、咨询配送都可以直接扫码联系。</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title">怎么找到我们</view>
      <view class="tag">意库 66 栋</view>
    </view>
    <image class="image route-preview" src="{{routeImage}}" mode="widthFix" bindtap="previewRoute"></image>
    <view class="muted mt-16">按路线图往前直走，暖心素火锅旁边就是店门口。点开图片可以放大查看。</view>
    <view class="muted mt-8">地址：{{shop.address}}</view>
    <view class="grid-2 mt-20">
      <view class="btn btn-ghost" bindtap="copyAddress">复制地址</view>
      <view class="btn" bindtap="callShop">拨打电话</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card signature-card">
    <view class="section-head signature-head">
      <view>
        <view class="section-title">招牌必点</view>
        <view class="muted">这几款是顾客最容易一试就回头的。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="tag">每日现炖</view>
    </view>
    <view class="signature-swiper-shell">
      <swiper
        class="signature-swiper"
        circular
        autoplay
        interval="4200"
        duration="420"
        current="{{currentSwiper}}"
        bindchange="handleSwiperChange"
      >
        <swiper-item wx:for="{{signatureSoups}}" wx:key="id">
          <view class="signature-slide">
            <image class="signature-image" src="{{item.image}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
            <view class="signature-mask"></view>
            <view class="signature-corner">{{item.badge}}</view>
            <view class="signature-content">
              <view class="signature-hot">{{item.hotLabel}}</view>
              <view class="signature-name">{{item.name}}</view>
              <view class="signature-desc">{{item.marketingLine}}</view>
              <view class="row space-between mt-20 align-start">
                <view class="signature-price-group">
                  <view class="signature-price">¥{{item.salePriceText}}</view>
                  <view class="signature-old-price">门市价 ¥{{item.originalText}}</view>
                </view>
                <view class="signature-stock">{{item.stock}} 份可点</view>
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </swiper-item>
      </swiper>
      <view
        wx:if="{{signatureSoups.length > 1}}"
        class="signature-arrow signature-arrow-left"
        hover-class="signature-arrow-hover"
        bindtap="prevSignature"
      >
        ‹
      </view>
      <view
        wx:if="{{signatureSoups.length > 1}}"
        class="signature-arrow signature-arrow-right"
        hover-class="signature-arrow-hover"
        bindtap="nextSignature"
      >
        ›
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="swiper-dots">
      <view
        wx:for="{{signatureSoups}}"
        wx:key="id"
        class="swiper-dot {{currentSwiper === index ? 'swiper-dot-active' : ''}}"
      ></view>
    </view>
    <view class="signature-note">每日现炖，售完即止</view>
    <view class="btn mt-20" bindtap="goTo" data-page="menu">去点招牌汤</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card fresh-visual-card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view>
        <view class="section-title">新鲜 · 现点现做</view>
        <view class="muted">视觉先让人心动，再决定下单。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="tag">看得到的新鲜感</view>
    </view>
    <view class="fresh-visual-grid">
      <view class="fresh-visual-main" wx:if="{{freshScenes[0]}}">
        <image class="fresh-visual-image main-image" src="{{freshScenes[0].image}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
        <view class="fresh-overlay"></view>
        <view class="fresh-overlay-text">
          <view class="fresh-overlay-tag">{{freshScenes[0].overlay}}</view>
          <view class="fresh-overlay-title">{{freshScenes[0].title}}</view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="fresh-visual-side">
        <block wx:for="{{freshScenes}}" wx:key="id">
          <view wx:if="{{index > 0}}" class="fresh-visual-side-item">
            <image class="fresh-visual-image side-image" src="{{item.image}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
            <view class="fresh-overlay"></view>
            <view class="fresh-overlay-text side-text">
              <view class="fresh-overlay-tag">{{item.overlay}}</view>
              <view class="fresh-overlay-title">{{item.title}}</view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </block>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title">联系店长</view>
      <view class="tag">售后 / 咨询</view>
    </view>
    <image class="contact-qr" src="{{ownerQrImage}}" mode="widthFix" bindtap="previewQr"></image>
    <view class="muted mt-12">如果要改单、确认配送或售后，直接扫码联系会更快。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="mask" wx:if="{{showOwnerModal}}" bindtap="closeOwnerModal"></view>
  <view class="owner-modal" wx:if="{{showOwnerModal}}">
    <view class="owner-title">店长验证</view>
    <view class="muted mt-12">请输入店长密码后进入后台。</view>
    <input
      class="input owner-input"
      password
      value="{{ownerCode}}"
      bindinput="bindOwnerCode"
      placeholder="请输入密码"
      placeholder-class="field-placeholder"
    />
    <view class="owner-actions">
      <view class="btn btn-ghost" bindtap="closeOwnerModal">取消</view>
      <view class="btn" bindtap="confirmOwnerAccess">进入后台</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
